---
import SectionHeader from "@/components/ui/section-header.astro"
---

<section class="section-wrapper pt-36 md:pt-40">
  {/* Top Header Section */}
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-6 text-center">
    <SectionHeader label="ABOUT US" isMain>
      We exist to make <br class="hidden md:block" />
      <span class="text-primary">home life easier</span>
    </SectionHeader>

    <p
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-delay="200"
      class="section-description max-w-2xl text-center"
    >
      THAZLO was born from a simple frustration: why should running out of gas
      or keeping clothes clean be this hard? We built the solution.
    </p>
  </div>

  {/* problem section */}
  <div class="mt-24 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-16 lg:mt-32">
    {/* heading */}
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h3
        data-aos="fade-right"
        data-aos-delay="240"
        class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-primary uppercase"
      >
        The Problem We Are Solving
      </h3>
      <h2
        data-aos="fade-right"
        data-aos-delay="300"
        class="font-heading text-3xl leading-tight font-bold text-pretty md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
      >
        88% of people are too busy to handle household chores efficiently
      </h2>
    </div>

    {/* right paragraphs */}
    <div
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-delay="300"
      class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground"
    >
      <p>
        Between demanding work schedules, family responsibilities, and daily
        commutes, millions of Nigerian households struggle with routine tasks
        like gas refills and laundry not because they're hard, but because time
        is scarce.
      </p>
      <p>
        THAZLO Innovations Limited was founded to bridge this gap, combining
        verified vendors, smart logistics and an intuitive app to make essential
        home services instantly accessible.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
